HB512 INTRODUCED
29 AN ACT
30
31 Relating to solid waste utility fees; to amend Sections
32 22-27-5 and 22-27-7, Code of Alabama 1975; to provide an
33 exclusive remedy for nonpayment of solid waste disposal
34 utility fees, charges, or rates; to revise the penalties for
35 failure to pay a solid waste disposal fee, charge, or rate;
36 and to make nonsubstantive, technical revisions to update the
37 existing code language to current style.
